== 限制區域許可 ==
雖然這些許可證通常由旅遊經營者安排，但沒有通過持有執照的旅遊經營者預訂的印度，孟加拉國和馬爾代夫遊客必須親自前往廷布的移民局辦理申請。許可證也可以在廷布的移民局辦理延期付費。孟加拉國，印度和馬爾代夫的公民在發放許可證和延長許可證方面免收費用。

== 提前獲得簽證 ==
{{TransH}}所有外国公民（孟加拉国，印度，马尔代夫除外）必须在入境不丹之前获得签证。在被批准的前提下，他们会被给予一张签证声明函（落地签证函）且必须在入境时呈予边检人员，此后签证将被印在护照上。外国公民必须雇佣一名有执照的不丹向导或者他们的国际合作者来提前预定签证与安排假期，每天的费用要求适用于在不丹停留的每一天。 其他国家的国民可以在首都[[廷布|廷布]]得到落地签证，但是必须在入境前续订好酒店及行程，并且保证每天至少消费250美元(旅遊旺季)或200美元(旅遊淡季)。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/faq|title=FAQ|publisher=|accessdate=11 June 2015|archive-date=2018-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318174844/http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/faq|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/travel-requirements|title=Travel Requirements|publisher=|accessdate=11 June 2015|archive-date=2018-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180320224857/http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/travel-requirements|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Discounts also apply for minors and larger groups while surcharges exist for groups smaller than 3. The minimum daily package required for visa processing covers accommodation, food, guide and vehicle with driver. Part of it goes towards [[Education_in_Bhutan|free education]], [[Health_in_Bhutan|free healthcare]] and poverty alleviation in Bhutan.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/faq|title=FAQ|publisher=|accessdate=11 June 2015|archive-date=2018-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318174844/http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/faq|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/visa|title=Visa|publisher=|accessdate=11 June 2015|archive-date=2018-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180408114419/http://www.tourism.gov.bt/plan/visa|dead-url=no}}</ref> Licensed tour guides accompany tourists during their trips and arrange accommodations - independent tourism by foreigners (except for citizens of [[孟加拉国|Bangladesh]], [[印度|India]], and [[马尔代夫|Maldives]]) is prohibited.

